I"P<div class="p">Will incidental lamentation win,</div>
<div class="p">And man's new fate intrinsically bound</div>
<div class="p">To once bedizening, ever hateful skin,</div>
<div class="p">Be proof 'gainst the eternal round on round,</div>
<div class="p">Till incidental lamentation's kin,</div>
<div class="p">Eternal lamentation on the ground</div>
<div class="p">Slogs where 'twas stricken from supernal wing,</div>
<div class="p">And all man in new woeful suit impound?</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Great Alexander's military might,</div>
<div class="p">Napoleon's French ego, ne'er subdued</div>
<div class="p">Such regions, such a never-ending site,</div>
<div class="p">As man's devices with his brains endued.</div>
<div class="p">Romance of plodding earth-round as a wight</div>
<div class="p">Defeated is in man's eternal feud</div>
<div class="p">With brains ingenious—emulous of God—</div>
<div class="p">After Lord Science for Dominion sued.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">And there is hope, but yet, if it be so,</div>
<div class="p">The time has come for glory, but first woe.</div>
